short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Invert Youtube Music like and dislike button to be like Youtube (Like first and dislike second).

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension invert the Youtube Music like and dislike buttons to be like on Youtube, the like first then the dislike. It was made for people who keep clicking on the dislike button instead of the like button (when disliking the music get skipped).
